overview:
HUAXIA TAIMAOBI CENTRE(S) was established in year 2003 by Mr Sam Fu, Till date, this is the only baby hair brush manufacturer company in Singapore. Having made 36000 baby hair brushes for more than 32000 newborn babies in the span of 9 years ,we have made a name for ourselves in both the local and expariat market.

Besides the complete baby hair brush service from cutting to collecting your baby hair for manufacturing at the convenience of your home, umbilical cord stamps, baby Chinese names selections and couple’s brush for new weds are also available.
